research_municipality_step.notes: The City of Dilley, Texas operates under a Mayor-Council government type, also referred to as a General Law Type A city in Texas. The current Mayor is Alexandria Inocencio, who was re-elected in May 2025. Alicia Machado serves as Mayor Pro Tem. The City Council members include Everardo Castillo Jr. (Place 1), Eric Aranda (Place 2), Ray Aranda (Place 4), and Rudy Alvarez (Place 5).
